Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:46.81,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}差し出す一手が勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.98,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}才能で勝利を呼ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.69,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HEFF1EA&\bord0}Save my life
